&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
  天授庵にて。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Temples" /><summary type="html">At Tenju-an Temple.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_A7R08321.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_A7R08321.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">More Maple &amp;amp; Bamboo・もみじ&amp;amp;竹</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220521/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="More Maple &amp;amp; Bamboo・もみじ&amp;amp;竹" /><published>2022-05-21T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-05-21T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/maple</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220521/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
