&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
  嵐山の竹林の前で、昼下がりの太陽に照らされるカエデの葉。天龍寺にて。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Foliage" /><category term="Tenryu-ji" /><category term="Bamboo Grove" /><summary type="html">Maple leaves lit by the late afternoon sun, in front of the Arashiyama bamboo grove. At Tenryu-ji Temple.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_IMG_5546.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_IMG_5546.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Togetsu Bridge・渡月橋</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220519/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Togetsu Bridge・渡月橋" /><published>2022-05-19T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-05-19T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/arashiyama</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220519/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Long exposure at dusk in Arashiyama. 
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
  嵐山の夕方の長時間露光。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Togetsu Bridge" /><summary type="html">Long exposure at dusk in Arashiyama.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_A7R08258.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_A7R08258.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Heian Jingu・平安神宮</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220518/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Heian Jingu・平安神宮" /><published>2022-05-18T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-05-18T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/heian-jingu</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220518/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Irises and water lilies at Heian Jingu’s Shinen Garden.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
  平安神宮神苑のかきつばたとスイレン。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Higashiyama" /><category term="Gardens" /><category term="Shrines" /><summary type="html">Irises and water lilies at Heian Jingu’s Shinen Garden.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_A7R08297.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_A7R08297.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Arashiyama Dusk・嵐山夕暮</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220517/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Arashiyama Dusk・嵐山夕暮" /><published>2022-05-17T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-05-17T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/arashiyama-dusk</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220517/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
The Katsura River in Arashiyama. Clouds don&apos;t usually light up like this in the evening, so it was a special treat after a day of overcast weather. Mt. Arashi &lt;em&gt;(Arashiyama)&lt;/em&gt; and the Togetsu Bridge are on the right side of this picture, a 24-shot HDR panorama.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
  嵐山の桂川です。普段、夕方に雲がこんな風に光ることはないので、曇り空の一日の後の特別な楽しみでした。この写真の右側が嵐山と渡月橋です。この写真は24枚撮りのHDRパノラマである。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Panoramas" /><category term="Togetsu Bridge" /><category term="Katsura River" /><summary type="html">The Katsura River in Arashiyama. Clouds don&apos;t usually light up like this in the evening, so it was a special treat after a day of overcast weather. Mt. Arashi (Arashiyama) and the Togetsu Bridge are on the right side of this picture, a 24-shot HDR panorama.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_A7R08242-HDR-Pano-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_A7R08242-HDR-Pano-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry></feed>